
netdiscover  can send the packet in the network enviroment , and sniff the packet , you can appoint your divice or filename to investigate the address network

useage:
				netdiscover -i eth0 -r 172.16.3.0/24

				passive mode:
								netdiscover -p 
								-p : sniff the around packet that go by myself

								when we keep in the sniff mode, we can use the keyword "h" to list the help reference for us
								the keyword "r" can assist us to list the arp request in local network

